snippet.title: Exelio Teaser 01 /  Tokyo Game Show 2024
snippet.description:
The first trailer for the crafting survival game "Exelio," unveiled at Tokyo Game Show 2024.

東京ゲームショウ2024で公開したクラフト系サバイバルゲーム「Exelio-エグゼリオ-」の予告編第1弾です。

Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2465510/

#indiegame #indiegames #indiegamedev #tokyogameshow
